{"tid":1408503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］天水圍被捕女子被帶走時扯到褲都甩埋","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T20:02:27.000Z","uid":169262,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"74b55bfec1b7ed896251dabe5763264b668fcf13","tid":1408503,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/99gveLk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F99gveLk.png&h=65fb7e08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多區爆發警民衝突，當中以將軍澳及觀塘最為嚴重，而同一時間，遠至新界西的天水圍亦有防暴警戒備！現場消息指，天水圍警署附近有近20架警車戒備，逾100名防暴警手持盾牌及警棍到場推進。現時警署對開約有100名居民聚集，據知一名女子早前在天耀邨涉嫌襲警，其後被防暴警拘捕並帶入警署。<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190805&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59897632\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190805%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59897632&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHaWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=b294c7f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190805%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59897632&h=c4b1bdd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190805&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59897632</a>"},{"pid":"b67bae196c3fd535a042c423fd3d3423344f17c7","tid":1408503,"uid":9845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:29:55.000Z","msg":"召喚女權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbed2722342173af1c7b62a6ca3074fdf6bb2cc","tid":1408503,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:30